title: Libreville named capital of anticorruption network (UNECA - United Nations Economic Commission for Africa)
text: ( Source : UNECA - United Nations Economic Commission for Africa ) The Gabonese capital has been chosen as seat of the Network of National Anti-Corruption Institutions in Central Africa (RINAC) after a three-day expert group meeting.
